# What is JavaScript?
JavaScript is the programming language that makes web pages interactive
and alive.

# Why We Use It
Without JavaScript, a website is just a static page of text and pictures. We use JavaScript to build things that move, change, or react when a user clicks, types, or hovers.

# The Real-Life House Example

